Do you need help with pre-registering to get the #COVID19 #vaccine?​
#CaritasLebanon's healthcare centers are ready to help you pre-register on the ministry of health’s online platform to get vaccinated, from Monday to Friday from 8AM to 2PM.​ @mophleb @WHOLebanon #Lebanon https://t.co/fW4GYeFyZi
